About US
.entry-header
WE ARE THE CLOSEST RV PARK TO ANY ENTRY POINT AT THE SPEEDWAY, PERIOD!!
Located just
456 steps
away from the Daytona International Speedway property,      Finish Line RV Park is open for most major events in the Daytona Beach Area , which includes the Daytona 500 and Speed Weeks, Bike Week, The Coke Zero Sugar 400, and Biketoberfest!
30 days a year, that’s it!!!
We offer Clean Hot Showers, 25 acres of Hardtop and tree covered sites, water throughout the park, Clean port-a-lets serviced daily, On-site pump truck, 24 hour security, and much much more. Sorry no tents.
Our location is walking distance to the Daytona International Speedway, Daytona USA and  ONE DAYTONA Entertainment Park  which includes BASS PRO SHOP, Cobbs Luxury Theatres, P.F. Chang’s, Four River’s BBQ, Rock Bottom Brewery, Ben & Jerry’s, Costco PLUS many stores for your shopping needs!! We are also close to the Richard Petty Driving Experience, Cracker Barrel Old Country Store, Hooters, 7-11, Carrabba’s  and much more. See map for location.
FinishLine RV Park has it all!
.entry-content

Events
.entry-header
Daytona International Speedway is the home of “The World’s Greatest Race” — the Daytona 500. Annually, the Daytona 500 attracts the largest audience in motorsports. If power is available it will be a 5 NIGHT MINIMUM.
OPEN February 6th through February 16th 2026 ONLY
From racing to swap meets to coleslaw wrestling, there is something for everyone at Daytona Bike Week. 3 Night Minimum for ANY Electric Site
Dates OPEN Feb 27th through March 8th 2026 ONLY
OPEN August 20th through August 23th, 2025 ONLY
OPEN October 16th through October 19th, 2025 ONLY
